headline: S&P 500 Gains and Losses Today: Moderna Stock Plunges After Resignation of FDA Vaccine Official
summary: The S&P 500 gained 0.6% on Monday, March 31, boosted by an afternoon rally even as investors brace for the planned onset of reciprocal tariffs later this week.

headline: AIG to Report First Quarter 2025 Financial Results on May 1, 2025, and Host Conference Call on May 2, 2025
summary: NEW YORK, March 31, 2025--American International Group, Inc. (NYSE: AIG) will report financial results for the first quarter ended March 31, 2025, after the market closes on Thursday, May 1, 2025. AIG’s press release and financial supplement will be available in the Investors section of AIG’s website at https://www.aig.com.
